window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>For years, the Shalador people suffered the cruelties of the corrupt queens who ruled them, forbidding their traditions, punishing those who dared show defiance, and forcing many more into hiding. Now that their land has been cleansed of tainted blood, the Rose-Jeweled Queen, Lady Cassidy, makes it her duty to restore it and prove her ability to rule. But even if Lady Cassidy succeeds, other dangers await.</p> <p> For the Black Widows see visions within their tangled webs that something is coming that will change the land - and Lady Cassidy - forever.</p>"; 
